  ('2e36a684-808b-4da5-a762-a65bfcb019fb', 'Night trains are the best way to travel', 'Flying is faster; night trains are better. You fall asleep in Lisbon and wake up in Prague with a window full of mountains. My ranking of sleeper routes, what to pack, and how to book berths without a local phone number. Slow travel is not slower, it is denser.'),
  ('2e36a684-808b-4da5-a762-a65bfcb019fb', 'Three weeks in Lisbon on a shoestring', 'I gave myself twenty-one days and a small budget in Lisbon. Slept in family-run guesthouses, ate at markets, took the slow ferry instead of the flight. The full cost breakdown, the neighborhood I would live in, and the one tourist trap that is actually worth it. Street photography set included.'),
